---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const CALENDLY_URL = 'https://calendly.com/derek-beitz-soloex/30min';

const pageDesc = 'Salesforce and HubSpot implementation, migration, and optimization. Scoped, architected, and delivered by the person who will actually build it - not a sales pitch.';
---

<Layout title="Services - Implement, Migrate, Optimize | Soloex.io" description={pageDesc} active="services">

  <section class="section-hero">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
      <h1>Three ways we fix CRMs.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Whether you're starting fresh, switching platforms, or cleaning up an inherited mess - we've done it 100+ times.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="implement">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-side">
          <div class="service-num">01</div>
          <h2>Implement</h2>
          <div class="service-sub">Start fresh. Build right.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-main">
          <p class="service-lead">Full Salesforce or HubSpot implementation from the ground up - scoped, architected, delivered. No abandoned half-builds. No "we'll figure it out in production."</p>
          <h3>What's included</h3>
          <ul class="bullets">
            <li>Discovery and requirements gathering</li>
            <li>Solution architecture and data model design</li>
            <li>Full build in Salesforce or HubSpot</li>
            <li>Custom workflows and automations</li>
            <li>Reports and dashboards</li>
            <li>User training and documentation</li>
            <li>Go-live support</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Best fit for</h3>
          <p>Companies standing up a CRM for the first time, or replacing a spreadsheet-and-email operation with a real system.</p>
          <a href={CALENDLY_URL} class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a free discovery call</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="hr-section" />

  <section id="migrate" class="section-tinted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-side">
          <div class="service-num">02</div>
          <h2>Migrate</h2>
          <div class="service-sub">Out of the old. Into what works.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-main">
          <p class="service-lead">Platform switches, data migrations, consolidation. Salesforce ↔ HubSpot, or from Zoho, Marketo, Eloqua, and other systems. Zero data loss. Minimal downtime.</p>
          <h3>What's included</h3>
          <ul class="bullets">
            <li>Source-system audit and field mapping</li>
            <li>Data cleanup before migration (not after)</li>
            <li>Historical record preservation</li>
            <li>Automation and workflow recreation in the new platform</li>
            <li>Integration re-wiring</li>
            <li>Phased cutover plan with rollback</li>
            <li>Post-migration validation</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Best fit for</h3>
          <p>Teams outgrowing their current tool, consolidating after an acquisition, or moving off a legacy system.</p>
          <a href={CALENDLY_URL} class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a free discovery call</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="hr-section" />

  <section id="optimize">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-block">
        <div class="service-side">
          <div class="service-num">03</div>
          <h2>Optimize</h2>
          <div class="service-sub">Fix what's broken. Keep what works.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-main">
          <p class="service-lead">CRM audits, workflow cleanup, reports and dashboards, admin support, and ongoing optimization. Make the system you already have do what it was supposed to do.</p>
          <h3>What's included</h3>
          <ul class="bullets">
            <li>CRM audit with prioritized recommendations</li>
            <li>Data cleanup and de-duplication</li>
            <li>Workflow and automation redesign</li>
            <li>Reports and dashboards</li>
            <li>Integration fixes (Zapier, Make.com, native)</li>
            <li>Admin support - milestone or retainer</li>
            <li>Team training</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Best fit for</h3>
          <p>Organizations whose CRM technically works but isn't delivering - slow reports, stale data, teams building workarounds.</p>
          <a href={CALENDLY_URL} class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a free discovery call</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-dark final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Not sure which one you need?</h2>
      <p class="final-cta-subhead">That's what the free 30-minute call is for. Tell us what's broken and we'll tell you honestly which path makes sense.</p>
      <a href={CALENDLY_URL} class="btn btn-light btn-large" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fix my CRM →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .lede {
    font-size: 19px;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-top: 18px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  .service-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .service-side { position: sticky; top: 96px; }
  .service-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-ink-500);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .service-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-ink-700);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .service-lead {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .service-main h3 {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-ink-500);
    margin: 24px 0 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .bullets {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .bullets li {
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .bullets li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 10px;
    width: 10px;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--color-ink-500);
  }

  .hr-section {
    border: 0;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .final-cta { text-align: center; padding: 96px 0; }
  .final-cta h2 { color: #FFFFFF; }
  .final-cta-subhead {
    color: var(--color-ink-300);
    font-size: 17px;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 18px auto 30px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .service-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .service-side { position: static; }
  }
</style>
